* She just waited there, seeing his reaction to her little prank. One that 
had gotten the reaction that she had hoped.
The acidic saliva which coated the inside of her mouth began to ooze down 
onto the top of Prowls hand, coating it with the gewy liquid.

But then she felt his hand begin to slowly move back over her tongue, 
thinking and wondering what to do next.
The bot side of her wanted to simply let him go, but the beast modes wanted 
to rip his arm clear off his shoulder.
So, again, the beast modes would dominate!

She suddenly snapped her jaws tighter down on Prowl's hand, right to the 
point that her teeth should go right through his armor and straight to the 
other side.
With swift movements she snapped her head to the side and suddenly raised to 
her hind legs, slamming both her clawed hands up against his shoulders to 
brace herself.*
